list.item:
About 1,000 men of the same detachment who were still in barracks 7 miles
                        east of Mukden mutinied August 26, reportedly killed their Japanese officers
                        and then decamped;

The Consulate General has been informed that Manchukuo troops (less than
                        one brigade) stationed 3 miles north of Mukden mutinied August 28, killed
                        their officers and decamped;
